    <item>
      <title>摩根大通分析师看跌中国科技股</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/jpmorgan-analyst-known-for-bearish-call-touts-china-tech-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位曾质疑中国科技股投资价值的分析师表示，中国科技股的涨幅超过了盈利，投资者预计企业将在经济好转的情况下实现盈利，然后再购买更多股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/jpmorgan-analyst-known-for-bearish-call-touts-china-tech-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 23:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国各地汽车经销商在遭受网络攻击后暂停服务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/cyberattack-hits-software-provider-for-car-dealers-across-the-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，在一个原本繁忙的假期里，美国主要汽车经销商软件提供商 CDK Global 发生网络事件，导致数千家汽车经销商陷入停顿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/cyberattack-hits-software-provider-for-car-dealers-across-the-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 19:29:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗银行认为，人工智能取代的金融岗位数量将超过其他任何行业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/citi-sees-ai-displacing-more-finance-jobs-than-any-other-sector</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团表示，人工智能可能会取代银行业比其他任何行业都多的就业岗位，因为这项技术将颠覆消费金融，并提高工人的工作效率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/citi-sees-ai-displacing-more-finance-jobs-than-any-other-sector</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 17:05:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
